    - rid: 6341597381389189120
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: Greeting
        text: 'Ahoy there chap. <pause=1>

          I see you''ve been washed ashore
          like I did many years ago.'
        position: {x: 800.05756, y: 143.3946}
        nextNodeID: WhereAreYouFrom
    - rid: 6341597381389189121
      type: {class: ChoiceNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: WhereAreYouFrom
        text: Do ye know where you came from?
        position: {x: 1118.2393, y: 84.51031}
        choices:
        - choiceText: I can't remember
          nextNodeID: NoWorries
        - choiceText: ...
          nextNodeID: NoWorries
        - choiceText: 
          nextNodeID: 
    - rid: 6341597381389189122
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: NoWorries
        text: 'No worries mate. Ye see, I got here many years ago after my ship ran
          ashore. The bloody captain must have had too much grog and hit some nasty
          cliff on our starboard. '
        position: {x: 842.41284, y: 598.9731}
        nextNodeID: NoWorries2
    - rid: 6341597381389189123
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: NoWorries2
        text: I've only just started to learn the ropes as a Jack back then. But
          those lovely people here were nearby and helped me ashore, otherwise I
          would have been in Davy Jones Locker with my fellow mates.
        position: {x: 1177.1235, y: 580.378}
        nextNodeID: Rehua
    - rid: 6341597381389189124
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: Rehua
        text: 'It must have been divine intervention, because they followed a shooting
          star and found myself on the way. It must have been in the will of Rehua,
          that they found me here. '
        position: {x: 254.72337, y: 103.57828}
        nextNodeID: Rehua2
    - rid: 6341597381389189125
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: Rehua2
        text: The stories differ from island to island, but I know him as one of
          the star gods and the brightest star on the southern hemisphere. Ye might
          know it in the Canis Majoris, as the star Sirius.
        position: {x: 325.92355, y: 381.9782}
        nextNodeID: UpForTheTask
    - rid: 6341597381389189126
      type: {class: ChoiceNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UpForTheTask
        text: Are ye going to sail in that old Waka to the next island? That sounds
          rough. Ye don't even have one for a dog watch. Are ye up for the task?
        position: {x: 669.82294, y: 368.0824}
        choices:
        - choiceText: I think so ...
          nextNodeID: SoundGood
        - choiceText: Can't wait!
          nextNodeID: SoundGood
    - rid: 6341597381389189127
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: SoundGood
        text: "Sounds convincing enough. \nBut before ye run off, I got something
          for ye."
        position: {x: 1026.7239, y: 384.3783}
        nextNodeID: Sextant
    - rid: 6341597381389189129
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: Sextant
        text: This is a Sextant. I found it in the remaining shipwrecks, that washed
          ashore. It should come in use if ye want to know which way ye want to sail.
          Focus on the stars and find the South Star to find yer nautical direction.
        position: {x: 1401.1233, y: 386.77826}
        nextNodeID: Bye
    - rid: 6341597381389189130
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: Bye
        text: If ye need any help with Star Constellations, I'll be here watching
          the star night. I am waiting on a sign from Rehua, to know why he saved
          me. If you see any signs from him out there, be sure tell me about them.
        position: {x: 1748.3232, y: 384.37823}
        nextNodeID: 
